ue\"><path d=\"M16.6 5.82a4.78 4.78 0 0 1-1.04-.65 4.7 4.7 0 0 1-1.7-3.17h-3.02v12.97a2.66 2.66 0 0 1-2.66 2.55 2.66 2.66 0 0 1-1.2-5.03 2.66 2.66 0 0 1 1.95-.18v-3.05a5.71 5.71 0 0 0-4.9 1.55 5.71 5.71 0 0 0 3.96 9.78 5.71 5.71 0 0 0 5.86-5.71V8.9a7.68 7.68 0 0 0 4.5 1.44V7.32a4.6 4.6 0 0 1-1.71-.5Z\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></div><main class=\"__variable_974415\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"@id\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/sobre#author\",\"name\":\"Ricardo Jorge\",\"jobTitle\":\"Fundador\",\"url\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/sobre\",\"worksFor\":{\"@id\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/#business\"},\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.instagram.com/elementgrouppt\",\"https://www.facebook.com/elementgroupdigital/\"]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Início\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Sobre\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/sobre\"}]}</script><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-bg pt-36 pb-24 px-6\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-10 right-0 w-[640px] h-[640px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(127,168,217,0.16), transparent 60%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-[1100px] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-5\">O porquê</p><h1 class=\"text-white tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.04]\">Nenhum bom negócio devia perder clientes por não ser <span class=\"text-accent\">encontrado online</span>.</h1><p class=\"mt-7 text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl\">É nisto que acredito desde o primeiro site que fiz para um amigo. As grandes agências são caras e distantes — e as PMEs merecem melhor. Foi por isso que criei a Element Group: dar aos pequenos negócios em Portugal uma presença online de topo, sem o preço nem a distância de uma agência. Trabalho a partir de Seia, na Serra da Estrela (distrito da Guarda), com clientes em todo o país.</p><p class=\"mt-8 text-xs text-muted flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-2.5 gap-y-1\"><span>Desde 2026</span><span class=\"text-dark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">·</span><span>Estúdio em Seia, Portugal</span><span class=\"text-dark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">·</span><span><span class=\"text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\">★</span> 5,0 no Google</span></p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col items-start sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-4\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/contacto\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Pedir orçamento grátis</span></a><a class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-white/90 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/portfolio\">Ver trabalhos<span class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"mt-12 flex items-center gap-4\"><span class=\"text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-signature)\">Ricardo Jorge</span><span class=\"h-8 w-px bg-white/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"text-xs text-dark leading-tight\">Fundador<br/>Element Group</span></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"relative max-w-[440px] mx-auto lg:ml-auto\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/5] rounded-[28px] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-[0_40px_90px_-30px_rgba(127,168,217,0.45)]\"><img alt=\"Ricardo Jorge, fundador da Element Group, no escritório\" fetchPriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-top\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 90vw, 440px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"absolute -left-3 sm:-left-6 bottom-8 hidden sm:flex flex-col gap-1 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-bg-card/85 backdrop-blur-md p-4 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.55)] max-w-[220px]\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-[#4f7fb8] text-black\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M5 12l5 5 9-10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span><p class=\"text-sm text-white font-medium\">Sem intermediários</p></div><p class=\"text-[11px] text-muted\">Falas sempre com quem faz o teu projeto.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-bg py-24 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"historia\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glow-drift absolute -left-40 top-1/3 -translate-y-1/2 w-[620px] h-[620px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(127,168,217,0.11), transparent 60%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#16191f] via-[#121317] to-[#0d0e11] shadow-[0_40px_90px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.7)] grid md:grid-cols-2 items-stretch\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-24 left-1/4 w-[440px] h-[440px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, rgba(127,168,217,0.20), transparent 60%)\"></div><div class=\"relative p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 self-start rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-3 py-1.5 mb-6\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-4 h-4\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fweb-app-manifest-512x512.png&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fweb-app-manifest-512x512.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fweb-app-manifest-512x512.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted\">A minha história</span></span><h2 id=\"historia\" class=\"text-white font-heading text-3xl md:text-[34px] font-medium tracking-[-0.02em] leading-tight\">Como (e porquê) começou</h2><div class=\"mt-6 space-y-4 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\"><p>Via sempre o mesmo: negócios bons — daqueles de confiança — escondidos atrás de um site fraco, ou sem presença nenhuma online. E as agências que podiam ajudar eram caras e distantes de mais para um pequeno negócio.</p><p>Comecei a fazer sites para amigos, quase como quem ajuda ao fim de semana. Mas os resultados apareciam — mais visitas, mais contactos, mais clientes. Aquilo que para mim era natural estava a mudar negócios reais.</p><p>Em 2026 deixei de o fazer como favor e passei a fazê-lo a sério. Nasceu a Element Group — para que qualquer PME em Portugal possa ter uma presença online de que se orgulha.</p></div><blockquote class=\"mt-8 border-l-2 border-accent/60 pl-5\"><p class=\"font-heading text-lg md:text-xl text-white leading-snug tracking-[-0.01em]\">“Um bom negócio nunca devia parecer pequeno online.”</p><footer class=\"mt-2 text-2xl text-white/90\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-signature)\">Ricardo Jorge</footer></blockquote></div><div class=\"relative min-h-[420px] md:min-h-0\"><img alt=\"Ricardo Jorge no escritório da Element Group\" fetchPriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 550px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-full.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-r from-[#121317] via-[#121317]/30 to-transparent md:via-[#121317]/45\"></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-24 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0d0e11]/70 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 right-4 md:bottom-auto md:top-6 md:right-6 flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-bg-card/85 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-3 shadow