relative max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4\">Em números</p><h2 id=\"numeros\" class=\"text-white\">Pequeno estúdio. Resultados a sério.</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Os números reais por trás da história — sem inflar nada.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"glow-card p-6 md:p-8 text-center\" style=\"animation-delay:0s\"><span class=\"glow-card__glow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"glow-card__ring\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div class=\"glow-card__content\"><div class=\"font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white tracking-[-0.02em] tabular-nums\"><span>0</span><span class=\"text-accent\">+</span></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-white font-medium\">Projetos entregues</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-dark\">desde 2026</p></div></div><div class=\"glow-card p-6 md:p-8 text-center\" style=\"animation-delay:-1.6s\"><span class=\"glow-card__glow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"glow-card__ring\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div class=\"glow-card__content\"><div class=\"font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white tracking-[-0.02em] tabular-nums\"><span>0,0</span><span class=\"text-accent\">★</span></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-white font-medium\">Avaliação no Google</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-dark\">9 avaliações</p></div></div><div class=\"glow-card p-6 md:p-8 text-center\" style=\"animation-delay:-3.2s\"><span class=\"glow-card__glow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"glow-card__ring\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div class=\"glow-card__content\"><div class=\"font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white tracking-[-0.02em] tabular-nums\"><span>2010</span></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-white font-medium\">Ano de fundação</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-dark\">o primeiro dia</p></div></div><div class=\"glow-card p-6 md:p-8 text-center\" style=\"animation-delay:-4.800000000000001s\"><span class=\"glow-card__glow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"glow-card__ring\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div class=\"glow-card__content\"><div class=\"font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white tracking-[-0.02em] tabular-nums\"><span>0,0</span><span class=\"text-accent\">×</span></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-white font-medium\">Mais tráfego orgânico</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-dark\">média dos projetos SEO</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg py-24 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"testemunhos\"><div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-3 py-1.5 mb-5\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h5v5c0 3-2 5-5 5v-2c1.7 0 3-1.3 3-3H7V7Zm9 0h5v5c0 3-2 5-5 5v-2c1.7 0 3-1.3 3-3h-3V7Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted\">Testemunhos</span></span><h2 id=\"testemunhos\" class=\"text-white\">O que fica é a relação</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Para além de um site bonito, o que os clientes guardam é como foi trabalhar comigo.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a2233] via-[#121620] to-[#0d0e11] p-8 md:p-12\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-20 left-1/4 w-[420px] h-[420px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, rgba(127,168,217,0.18), transparent 60%)\"></div><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-5 left-7 font-heading text-[90px] leading-none text-accent/20 select-none\">“</span><div class=\"relative min-h-[210px] md:min-h-[190px] flex items-center\"><blockquote style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)\"><p class=\"text-white text-lg md:text-2xl font-heading font-medium leading-snug tracking-[-0.01em]\">Desde o primeiro dia senti que falava com alguém que se importava mesmo com o meu negócio — e não com mais um cliente. Explicou tudo sem complicar e esteve sempre disponível.</p><footer class=\"mt-7 flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-[#4f7fb8] text-white font-heading font-semibold text-sm\">CE</span><div><p class=\"text-white text-sm font-medium leading-tight\">Cliente Element Group</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-muted\">Negócio local · Portugal</p></div></footer></blockquote></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-bg to-[#08090b] py-28 px-6\" aria-labelledby=\"conversar\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bottom-0 w-[760px] h-[420px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgba(127,168,217,0.20), transparent 70%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-5\">O próximo passo</p><h2 id=\"conversar\" class=\"text-white\">Vamos conversar sobre o teu negócio?</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto\">Conta-me o que tens em mente — sem compromisso e sem pressão. Respondo-te pessoalmente, normalmente em menos de 2 horas.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-5\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/contacto\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Vamos conversar</span></a><span class=\"text-sm text-white/70\">ou escreve-me para<!-- --> <a class=\"text-white/90 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"mailto:info@elementgroup.pt\">info@elementgroup.pt</a></span></div><div class=\"mt-14 flex items-center justify-center gap-3\"><img alt=\"Ricardo Jorge\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover object-top border border-white/10\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"text-left\"><span class=\"block text-2xl text-white/90 leading-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-signature)\">Ricardo Jorge</span><span class=\"block text-[11px] text-dark mt-1\">Fundador · Element Group</span></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-[#08090b] border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10 px-6\"><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-12 mb-16\"><div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2.5\" aria-label=\"Eleme